i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyD7Aqr.png&h=4d0ecdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVq3b2xUJyAGBQLCNh58qd4orr7Aa8pcEDhCjw2WNAKM?filename=0JQqAgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JQqAgq.png&h=b5d58552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>人類與生俱來就有控蘿莉既魂 係差在覺醒左未 好似係</blockquote><br />\nBy小坂井綾<br />\n<blockquote>體型蘿都係蘿，可以抱住黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBy金閃閃<br />\n<br />\n問: Are you Lolicon?<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNZxaTD9S7wFe7gj6zzTGLzZB2PNJLzTEbFrjoJ2L64ws?filename=bnwVG1L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnwVG1L.png&h=4a42415a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nyes i am<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPe5HFmxdSU3bXLtBbHB3YKZisfy9C2zSjDasahBpBYaq?filename=Lwgjjqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLwgjjqc.png&h=15200f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nloli is cute<br />\nBy持續比牙井關心嘅Husky<br />\n<br />\n以下係腳膠部部長鈴木佳奈(<span class=\"red\"><del>P</del></span>)致辭時間<br />\ngal台腳膠分部長鄭重聲明踐踏play乃腳膠玩法之中不可分裂的一部分，本分部正告哈士奇，任何企圖破壞腳膠社會繁榮穩定、阻礙腳膠發展的圖謀都不會得逞，到頭來只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳。對於哈士奇干涉腳膠內政、損害腳膠利益的行徑，本分部必將採取有力措施堅決反制。任何人都不要低估腳膠部維護主權、安全、發展利益的堅定決心。腳膠部堅持對外開放，互利共贏，同世界分享玩腳發展的機遇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gExuy5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgExuy5G.png&h=4eb90947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcMQr28u9wtgxdwGqnfzkZ5nS5YhHZjEZ4qt62ihARpHA?filename=tjTSLP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtjTSLP5.jpg&h=770915e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">NO, I am腳膠</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRVakJF5ZXksQfkNRDUhwpvHXPY6BNGBXm5pB2FeEo75J?filename=a2REqPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2REqPZ.jpg&h=fb29b303&s={SIZE}\"